The holiday of Barbie and her sister Skipper, Stacie and Chelsea gets an unexpected turn during the holidays. After their plane by a snow storm is diverted, the girls find themselves far from their planned dream vacation in New York. Stranded in a remote inn in the small town Tannenbaum see their dream vacation even more in the water. But soon they experience magic moments and are hospitably welcomed by new friends. Thanks for the overwhelming reception, they put their musical talents to provide a performance for the entire city. The girls quickly see that just being together the most important thing for a perfect Christmas celebration.
From November 15 to rent

